snippet.title: Diana and new Cinderella story
snippet.description:
Cinderella story for kids by Diana and Roma. 
Diana, like Cinderella, she really wants to go to the ball. But Brother Roma makes a mess at home and makes her do the cleaning. It’s good that a fairy godmother appears in time, which will add a little bit of toys and magic to this story.
Diana`s INSTAGRAM https://www.instagram.com/kidsdianashow/
